TITLE: 商品情報
BODY_SQL:
SELECT
SAMPLE_MST_ITEM.ITEM_CODE as ITEM_CODE
\,SAMPLE_MST_ITEM.ITEM_NM as ITEM_NM
\,SAMPLE_MST_ITEM.SMPL_ITEM_KBN as SMPL_ITEM_KBN
\,SAMPLE_MST_ITEM.ITEM_SIZE as ITEM_SIZE
\,SAMPLE_MST_ITEM.SMPL_SIZE_KBN as SMPL_SIZE_KBN
FROM          SAMPLE_MST_ITEM
